description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 75, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 225, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 8 for East, 8 for South, and 3 for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10753-78830-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [225 Votes, Top 5% Score]
